ğŸ¯ Overview
Trenzzo is a comprehensive multi-vendor e-commerce solution built with the MERN stack. It provides a seamless shopping experience for customers while offering powerful management tools for sellers and administrators. The platform features real-time notifications, secure payment processing, and a responsive, modern UI.

âœ¨ Key Highlights
âœ… Multi-vendor architecture with role-based access control

âœ… Real-time order notifications via Socket.IO

âœ… Secure OTP authentication using Resend API

âœ… Test mode payments with Razorpay integration

âœ… Cloudinary-powered media management

âœ… Responsive design with Tailwind CSS & ShadCN/UI

âœ… Optimized performance with TanStack Query

